Module dual.engine.if.expression.

Rule classify given amount, produce:
  Return if amount greater than 10000 then "large" else if amount greater than 1000 then "medium" else "small".

Rule gradeWithLet given score, produce:
  Let tier be if score greater than 90 then "A" else if score greater than 70 then "B" else "C".
  Return tier.
